    "name": "Stick Out!",
    "steam_appid": 4149750,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "controller_support": "full",
    "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/4c2784b6e3511922c797ac73015fe7f8.poster.avif?t=1770329269\" width=1000 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/4c2784b6e3511922c797ac73015fe7f8.webm?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/4c2784b6e3511922c797ac73015fe7f8.mp4?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stick Out!</strong> Es un juego de plataformas de precisión donde debes usar una lanza para sortear obstáculos clavándote a las paredes y superficies. ¡Recoge monedas, compra aspectos, obten estrellas y rompe los records de tiempo! ¿Puedes completar cada nivel?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/38fefa724a8c4758c3f185f07f2a9cef.poster.avif?t=1770329269\" width=1008 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/38fefa724a8c4758c3f185f07f2a9cef.webm?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/38fefa724a8c4758c3f185f07f2a9cef.mp4?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>El arte del Stick-Jumping</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >¡<strong>Engancha</strong>, <strong>carga</strong> y <strong>suelta</strong>! Domina esta habilidad para avanzar y superar cada nivel. Cuanto más cargues tu salto, más alto llegarás. Encuentra el equilibrio perfecto para lograr el salto que necesitas, pero no te confíes: estos obstáculos pueden ser peligrosos...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/9a1769a0e5b36671b431aaf8ebb7af1d.poster.avif?t=1770329269\" width=1008 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/9a1769a0e5b36671b431aaf8ebb7af1d.webm?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/9a1769a0e5b36671b431aaf8ebb7af1d.mp4?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>¡Mundos por explorar!</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explora más de 50 niveles repartidos en 6 mundos únicos, cada uno con su propia temática y mecánicas especiales. Pon a prueba tus habilidades de plataformas, descubre las mejores rutas y rompe los récords de tiempo en cada nivel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/b95b345a46dee7b2e8271ad0b253fd07.poster.avif?t=1770329269\" width=1008 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/b95b345a46dee7b2e8271ad0b253fd07.webm?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/b95b345a46dee7b2e8271ad0b253fd07.mp4?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>Personaliza tu Personaje</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recolecta monedas en cada nivel para desbloquear una gran variedad de colores, patrones exóticos, lanzas distintivas y estilos de ojos únicos. Personaliza tu personaje a tu manera mientras te conviertes en el mejor Stick-Jumper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/346241bdd6659bcd7bfe8104b003b587.poster.avif?t=1770329269\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/346241bdd6659bcd7bfe8104b003b587.webm?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/346241bdd6659bcd7bfe8104b003b587.mp4?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
    "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/4c2784b6e3511922c797ac73015fe7f8.poster.avif?t=1770329269\" width=1000 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/4c2784b6e3511922c797ac73015fe7f8.webm?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/4c2784b6e3511922c797ac73015fe7f8.mp4?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stick Out!</strong> Es un juego de plataformas de precisión donde debes usar una lanza para sortear obstáculos clavándote a las paredes y superficies. ¡Recoge monedas, compra aspectos, obten estrellas y rompe los records de tiempo! ¿Puedes completar cada nivel?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/38fefa724a8c4758c3f185f07f2a9cef.poster.avif?t=1770329269\" width=1008 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/38fefa724a8c4758c3f185f07f2a9cef.webm?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/38fefa724a8c4758c3f185f07f2a9cef.mp4?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>El arte del Stick-Jumping</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >¡<strong>Engancha</strong>, <strong>carga</strong> y <strong>suelta</strong>! Domina esta habilidad para avanzar y superar cada nivel. Cuanto más cargues tu salto, más alto llegarás. Encuentra el equilibrio perfecto para lograr el salto que necesitas, pero no te confíes: estos obstáculos pueden ser peligrosos...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/9a1769a0e5b36671b431aaf8ebb7af1d.poster.avif?t=1770329269\" width=1008 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/9a1769a0e5b36671b431aaf8ebb7af1d.webm?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/9a1769a0e5b36671b431aaf8ebb7af1d.mp4?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>¡Mundos por explorar!</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explora más de 50 niveles repartidos en 6 mundos únicos, cada uno con su propia temática y mecánicas especiales. Pon a prueba tus habilidades de plataformas, descubre las mejores rutas y rompe los récords de tiempo en cada nivel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/b95b345a46dee7b2e8271ad0b253fd07.poster.avif?t=1770329269\" width=1008 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/b95b345a46dee7b2e8271ad0b253fd07.webm?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/b95b345a46dee7b2e8271ad0b253fd07.mp4?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>Personaliza tu Personaje</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recolecta monedas en cada nivel para desbloquear una gran variedad de colores, patrones exóticos, lanzas distintivas y estilos de ojos únicos. Personaliza tu personaje a tu manera mientras te conviertes en el mejor Stick-Jumper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/346241bdd6659bcd7bfe8104b003b587.poster.avif?t=1770329269\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/346241bdd6659bcd7bfe8104b003b587.webm?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4149750/extras/346241bdd6659bcd7bfe8104b003b587.mp4?t=1770329269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
